# Parking Lot Problem - DKatalis

### Specifications

* Runtime: Node.js
* Language: TypeScript (and view of JavaScript)
* JavaScript Testing Framework : Jest

## Structure

* parking_lot_2.0.0
  * bin
  * functional_spec
  * src
    * main
    * test
    * controller



## Installation

```
$ npm install

```

## Test

```
$ npm test

```

## Build

```
$ npm run build

```

## Start

if using file as input
```
$ npm run start {file_input.txt}
```

if using user input command
```
$ npm run start
```

or

```
$ node built/app.js {file_input.txt}
```



## Functional Test (Aruba)

You can run the full suite from `parking_lot` by doing

```
parking_lot $ bin/run_functional_tests
```

You can run the full suite directly from `parking_lot/functional_spec` by doing

```
parking_lot/functional_spec $ bundle exec rake spec:functional
